name: EEG Beauty
body:
### The Point
There are two points to this: 1) to make Lara Pantlin a nice EEG processing toolbox, and 2) to help Michelle Maiden learn how to use GitHub. If you do not fall under either of these points, please email me at Michelle.Maiden@Colorado.edu.

### Authors and Contributors
This was made by Michelle Maiden (@mdotmaid).
